<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171764>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Part of hypopygium (A, C) and gonostylus (B, D), ventral view. A, B, Keilbachia apprima sp. n. (holotype). C, D, K. demissa sp. n. (holotype). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171764/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171765>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Keilbachia arrecta sp. n. (holotype). Part of hypopygium (A) and gonostylus (B) and subapical megaseta and two ordinary setae of gonostylus (C), ventral view. Scale for A and B 0.10 mm, for C 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171765/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171768>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Part of hypopygium (A, C), tegmen (D) and gonostylus (B, E), ventral view. A, B, Keilbachia arcuata sp. n. (holotype). C – E, K. aculeata sp. n. (holotype). Scale for A – C and E 0.10 mm, for D 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171768/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171767>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Part of hypopygium (A, C) and gonostylus (B, D), ventral view. A, B, Keilbachia tenuicula sp. n. (holotype). C, D, K. mira sp. n. (holotype). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171767/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171766>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Part of hypopygium (A, C) and gonostylus (B, D), ventral view. A, B, Keilbachia scutica sp. n. (holotype). C, D, K. flagrispina Mohrig (from Burma). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171766/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

